msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 37 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 37 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamapeyyālavagga "
msgstr "1. Abbreviated Texts "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4. Tīhidhammehisutta → tīhi (pts1)
msgctxt "sn37.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Tīhidhammehisutta "
msgstr "4. Three Qualities "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.240, sc1
msgctxt "sn37.4:1.1"
msgid "“Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo yebhuyyena kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when females have three qualities, when their body breaks up, after death, they are mostly reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

msgctxt "sn37.4:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi? "
msgstr "What three? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.4:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, mātugāmo pubbaṇhasamayaṃ maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati. "
msgstr "A female lives at home with a heart full of the stain of stinginess in the morning, jealousy in the afternoon, and sexual desire in the evening. "

msgctxt "sn37.4:1.4"
msgid "Majjhanhikasamayaṃ issāpariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn37.4:1.5"
msgid "Sāyanhasamayaṃ kāmarāgapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.4:1.6"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo yebhuyyena kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr "When females have these three qualities, when their body breaks up, after death, they are mostly reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.4:1.7"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr " "

